asnu01 – Injector cleaning servicing

ASNU-01  Classic GDI Injector Servicing and Cleaning Machine.

The ASNU Classic GDI Features

 

    • • Backlit Viewing Window
    • • Multi Language Selection
    • • Digital Operational Display
    • • Membrane Key Pad
    • • Wide Range of Functions
    • • Injector Shot Counter Display
    • • Injector Shot Timer Display
      • • Duty Cycle Display ASNU 01
    • • Lbs per Hour to Milliliters Calculator
    • • Manual & Automatic Cleaning Cycles
    • • Suitable for Injected Motorcycles
    • • Suitable for Injected Marine Engines
    • • Suitable for LPG Injection
    • • For use one EVERY type of Manifold Injector
    • • Easy to Read LCD Screen

Please contact ASNU HQ if you are in the UK or your nearest ASNU distributor if you are outside of the UK and wish to purchase any ASNU products.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=”1/2″][vc_single_image image=”3009″ img_size=”large” css=””][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row custom_css_code=”LmdlbS1idXR0b24tc2l6ZS1tZWRpdW0lN0IlMEElMjAlMjAlMjAlMjBtaW4td2lkdGglM0EyMjdweCUzQiUwQSUyMCUyMCUyMCUyMG1hcmdpbiUzQTIwcHglM0IlMEElN0Q=”][vc_column]
